OL,6,FA new government vision for inclusive
OL,7,Flearning has been unveiled to parents
OL,8,Fand children but it is expected to
OL,9,Ftake a decade to achieve fully.
OL,11,FJersey's Education Minister Rob Ward
OL,12,Fsays: "That's a reality and I think
OL,13,Fit's important that we spell that out.
OL,14,FYou can't make the changes overnight
OL,15,Fto be as inclusive as we want to be
